85.50點；納指跌72.55點，跌幅為0.34%，報21100.31點；昨日恒指收報25104,跌61點,成交縮減至2394億,指數開市時段於25100水位窄幅牛皮波動,午後突下試25000,兩天內第二次下試該水位,市場氣氛轉趨擔心,觀望及減貨聲音上升。指數雖處於5,10,20天線以下,就圖表上觀察,沿著50天線上升趨勢無變,經歷兩天守穩25000水位,指數傾向一波波向上升,且看美國央行年會（jackson holes meeting)會否給力恒指進一步上破25500阻力。&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32013329&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=170420422368a7cf964bf3d2_28079343"/><published>2025-08-22T07:58:30+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>5b3b3ffbce08b226eefb79ac24290def</id><title>IG不尋常急跌中，大家小心！</title><updated>2025-08-22T08:53:37+08:00</updated><author><name>籃球界股神</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-22T08:53:37+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573688706"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573688706"&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16446173" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="573688706" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250822/20250822_f656a4baaaf3d05cdd97E1mkyUsM9rMv.jpg"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/1ee31f/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250822/20250822_f656a4baaaf3d05cdd97E1mkyUsM9rMv.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16446173_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16446173&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Screenshot_2025-08-22-07-52-38-980_com.android.chrome.jpg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (187.29 KB)&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-8-22 08:53&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/im